{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-16_end","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":31,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-16_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"JT8-2","storyName":"睁眼，便是日暮","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"阿米娅积攒了足够的情绪。愤怒积攒已久，不属于她的记忆冲破了她对自己的限制，她的力量终被情感同化。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-16_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-16","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":29,"next":31,"characters":["塔露拉？","陈","阿米娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":3},{"type":"Dialog","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_topburning","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$towerfierce_intro","key":"$towerfierce_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fireburst","volume":"1","text":"","id":9},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$burningloop1","volume":"1","loop":"true","text":"","id":10},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":12},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":13},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing1","id":14},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":17},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing1","id":18},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":21},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing2","id":22},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":25},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":26},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":27},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":30},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"还不够。这样是不能战胜我的火的。","id":33,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"哈，哈......","id":35,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"无智亦无勇。什么人会喜欢这种演出？","id":37,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"陈晖洁，你要为别人挥剑到何时？你有哪怕一次为自己拔出过那把剑吗？","id":38,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"魔王，哈哈......也许诸王庭搞出了一个残劣的次品。","id":39,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"还不够。还不够，两位。","id":40,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"Character","id":43},{"type":"Text","text":"不，已经够了。","id":44},{"type":"Dialog","id":45},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"再在我脑中说话，我就要将你请出我的思绪了。","id":48,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"已经足够了。","id":50,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈长官的情感......","id":51,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"从赤霄那里流向了我。","id":52,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"以前，我们两个人是没有关联的。是发生在这里的事情将我们联系在了一起，是我们感染者的命运将我们推向这里......","id":53,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"因为我们都认定这片大地的明天，理应比今天更好。","id":54,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"晖洁和你不是一种人，卡特斯。","id":56,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"罗德岛只是各个政治实体的稻草人，你会为了他们去杀害同胞，装出良善的模样，等待一个制造混乱谋取利益的时机。你们完全不在乎感染者。","id":57,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你还想绑架谁？你还想让陈长官相信你那些谎言吗？","id":59,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你通过塔露拉绑架了整合运动，你用切尔诺伯格绑架了乌萨斯军队，让利益绑架了乌萨斯人，现在你还想绑架谁？！","id":60,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"识破你的谎言也很简单，因为你只说结果与动机，却从不说会发生什么！你对塔露拉的许诺也是相同的！","id":61,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"哦......","id":63,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你答应陈长官和整合运动说要让感染者有一片可以居住的地方，答应一场大战之后感染者终将崛起，可是，如果是塔露拉，她是不会再许诺的。","id":65,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"因为当时的那个承诺已经伤她够深了......","id":66,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅！","id":68,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈长官......？","id":70,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅......我有些后悔。要是早点认识你，也许很多事情都会不一样。","id":72,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但很多错我已经犯下了。","id":73,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我想，那时候的陈长官，也不一定会认同我现在的想法。","id":75,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"不是长官了。叫我陈。","id":77,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈小姐。","id":79,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"也行，这样正式点。会不会太正式了？","id":81,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"不好意思，让你看见我们姐妹那么难看的那一面。我以为我们的重逢会更戏剧性些......或者更俗套些的。","id":82,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我觉得再怎么俗套，当久别重逢以后，我们的感情就是一样的。","id":84,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"流泪很俗套吗？我不觉得。普通人都会流泪。","id":85,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"口才不错，卡特斯。情感攻势也拿捏得很准。","id":87,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"不过，雄辩当用来说服王庭与元老院，征服议会与摇摆不定的软蛋，煽动盲目的军士与暴躁的领民......而不是用来说服我。","id":88,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"“卡兹戴尔三次毁于大火。它数次得重建，得千万新血，得王庭盘踞，只是先前住民皆已身化灰烬，随风而去。”","id":89,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"在切城时，你曾举起一面屏障，拦下我的呼吸......我放走了你，因为为你牺牲的英勇战士当得尊崇。","id":90,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"但现在，你已得我注视。你不再有机会逃走了。","id":91,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"活过一场火焚吧，卡特斯。","id":92,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"糟了......！阿米娅！快来我这里！","id":94,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"我在与她对话，而不是你，妹妹。现在——","id":96,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"——闻闻烧焦的她会是什么味。","id":97,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅！！","id":99,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","id":100},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":101},{"type":"Dialog","id":102},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":103},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.5","Delay":"0.4","id":104},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":105},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":106},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.4","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.4","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.1","afrom":"1","rfrom":"1","gfrom":"0.4","bfrom":"0.4","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0.8","rfrom":"1","gfrom":"1","bfrom":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":112},{"type":"Character","id":113},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_23","x":"0","y":"20","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":115},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":116},{"type":"Character","id":117},{"type":"ImageTween","yFrom":"20","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"40","block":"false","id":118},{"type":"Text","text":"烈焰自无形化作有形，白色的火浪呼啸着自四面八方扑向阿米娅，将她与她所踩的地面彻底包裹。","id":119},{"type":"Dialog","id":120},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"0","id":122},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":123},{"type":"Dialog","id":124},{"type":"Character","id":125},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你！","id":127,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你试试看，你如果现在出剑，会不会把我的法术和她一起切开？","id":129,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"放开她！塔露拉，放开她！你想杀的人是我！","id":131,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"太迟了。","id":133,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":134},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"Character","id":136},{"type":"Text","text":"三分钟已经到了。时间已经够了。","id":137},{"type":"Text","text":"她们的思绪跨过了龙门与切尔诺伯格，她们的记忆越过了北部荒原与乌萨斯的土地。","id":138},{"type":"Text","text":"自己已经厘清了陈的想法。自己已经把陈的战斗全都浓聚在此。自己已经把龙门与切尔诺伯格，以及北原上的一切烙在身上。","id":139},{"type":"Dialog","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":143},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":144},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":147},{"type":"Text","text":"黑色的线条自焰球内喷涌而出，继而收束成形，在焰球上划开裂口。","id":148},{"type":"Text","text":"白焰忽尔消失。","id":149},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"......怎么......","id":151,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"是什么切开了焰狱......？","id":152,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":153},{"type":"Character","id":154},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":156},{"type":"Dialog","id":157},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅剧烈地喘息着。","id":159},{"type":"Text","text":"她闭上眼。","id":160},{"type":"Text","text":"许多想法在阿米娅的脑海中成型，又迅速散去。","id":161},{"type":"Character","id":162},{"type":"Dialog","id":163},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_light","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":164},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"$loneliness_loop","volume":"0.4","id":165,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":167},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":168},{"type":"Text","text":"她记得霜星咬牙切齿的悲鸣。","id":169},{"type":"Character","id":170},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":171},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见温迪戈屹立不倒的遗躯。","id":172},{"type":"Character","id":173},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":174},{"type":"Text","text":"她听过阿丽娜压抑不住的轻呼。","id":175},{"type":"Character","id":176},{"type":"Character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_026","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":177},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见Ace与Scout，想起精英干员们在酒会上跳舞。","id":178},{"type":"Character","id":179},{"type":"Text","text":"她也想起丽萨从烤箱里端出姜饼，想起米米的手工小胸牌，看见稚日在走道停电时胸口亮起的微弱的光和他傻笑着的雀斑脸。","id":180},{"type":"Text","text":"她想起爸爸和妈妈。","id":181},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见妈妈帮她稳住琴弓时托住她肩膀的手，妈妈的手指白皙又修长，但伤疤和老茧蹭得她有些难受。","id":182},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见爸爸把她推出门外后摔落下去，她想不起爸爸说了什么，只记得他眼带泪花，说了声再见，活下去，阿米娅。","id":183},{"type":"Character","id":184},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_056","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":185},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见特蕾西娅将剑刺入自己胸膛。","id":186},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见特蕾西娅说了声晚安后关上了灯。","id":187},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见特蕾西娅为她挑了件白色的衣裳，笑得比自己还开心。","id":188},{"type":"Character","id":189},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_048","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":190},{"type":"Text","text":"她看见博士走在她身前。她看见博士回头，等她走到身旁，才继续迈步。","id":191},{"type":"Character","id":192},{"type":"Dialog","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":194},{"type":"Dialog","id":195},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":196},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她看见一个萨卡兹。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":197},{"type":"Subtitle","id":198},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"大火。同样也是大火。烧光一切却烧不尽恶意的大火。本就诞生自邪恶的大火。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":199},{"type":"Subtitle","id":200},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"同样也是被大火包围的营帐里，那个萨卡兹高声咆哮。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":201},{"type":"Subtitle","id":202},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我们又被背叛了！他们撕毁了协约，他们突袭了我们的驻地！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":203},{"type":"Subtitle","id":204},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那只是些普通的人，那些不是士兵！那只是些普通的萨卡兹人！！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":205},{"type":"Subtitle","id":206},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"为什么要杀死我的妻儿？为什么我的子民要受到如此不公的待遇？！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":207},{"type":"Subtitle","id":208},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"为什么不允许我们活下去？！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":209},{"type":"Subtitle","id":210},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我们只是想要一片安宁的土地！我们只是想要找个地方生活！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":211},{"type":"Subtitle","id":212},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"只因为我们是萨卡兹吗？！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":213},{"type":"Subtitle","id":214},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅的泪滴在火焰中蒸发。","id":215},{"type":"Text","text":"只因为我们是感染者吗？阿米娅问到。","id":216},{"type":"Dialog","id":217},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"只因为我们是萨卡兹，我们就是铁石心肠就是牲畜不如，就不该在这大地上活下去了吗？","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":218},{"type":"Subtitle","id":219},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那个萨卡兹的吼声刺透了焰舌，刺透了法术，刺透了时代。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":220},{"type":"Subtitle","id":221},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们做过什么坏事？他们不是无辜的吗？！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":222},{"type":"Subtitle","id":223},{"type":"Text","text":"你恨他们吗？阿米娅轻声问。","id":224},{"type":"Dialog","id":225},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"记忆是不会回答的。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":226},{"type":"Subtitle","id":227},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但高大的萨卡兹仿佛知晓一定会有人问出这个问题般说了下去。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":228},{"type":"Subtitle","id":229},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"不，或许他自己就不断地在问自己这个问题——","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":230},{"type":"Subtitle","id":231},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们恨我们吗？！无来由地残害我们的同胞，允诺后反悔，为了掩盖罪恶犯下更大的罪恶！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":232},{"type":"Subtitle","id":233},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"这是玩弄，还是操控？这是逐利还是单纯的虐待？这是他们一时的偏执，还是骨子里的恶毒？","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":234},{"type":"Subtitle","id":235},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们该恨的是我们吗？","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":236},{"type":"Subtitle","id":237},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他们应该要恨他们自己，恨自己把自己的这片土地变成这种样子，把我们所有人都变成了恶棍！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":238},{"type":"Subtitle","id":239},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹拿起了剑。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":240},{"type":"Subtitle","id":241},{"type":"Text","text":"黑色与青色浸透了长剑的每个部分，那重量压在阿米娅的肩上，那长剑握在阿米娅手里。","id":242},{"type":"Dialog","id":243},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"我恨他们吗？","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":244},{"type":"Subtitle","id":245},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"愤怒。愤怒。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":246},{"type":"Subtitle","id":247},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"无止境的愤怒，对这片大地上一切痛苦与不公的愤怒。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":248},{"type":"Subtitle","id":249},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"冲破了萨卡兹的底线，冲破了阿米娅的心防。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":250},{"type":"Subtitle","id":251},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"憎恨连仇怨都杀不死，养育恶意的东西怎么能战胜恶意？","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":252},{"type":"Subtitle","id":253},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但是......怒火是不一样的。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":254},{"type":"Subtitle","id":255},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"即使我不报复也不怀恨，我也有永远愤怒下去的权力！萨卡兹怒吼到。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":256},{"type":"Subtitle","id":257},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果他们没想过这个结局，他们就不该这样做！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":258},{"type":"Subtitle","id":259},{"type":"Dialog","id":260},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":261},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"火焰在他的吼叫中颤动不止，它们畏缩，自嘲弄的橙色转化成青色。青色的火焰越烧越旺。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":262},{"type":"Subtitle","id":263},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"萨卡兹拔出长剑，那把剑长且锋利，蓝色的气焰顺着黑色的剑身滑落。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":264},{"type":"Subtitle","id":265},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他的怒火随之高涨。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":266},{"type":"Subtitle","id":267},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果这就是结果的话，来吧！我就把这个结果带给你们！带给我们所有人......带给我自己！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":268},{"type":"Subtitle","id":269},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"如果这片大地不准我放下武器，那我只能拿起剑奋战，直到末日！","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":270},{"type":"Subtitle","id":271},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":272},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":273},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅知道，在杀死所有背誓者后，这个高大的萨卡兹自尽了。","id":274},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅也知道，这把剑随后化作飞灰，仿佛不曾存在过。","id":275},{"type":"Text","text":"但这个萨卡兹君王的青色愤怒，早已和他的经历一起，成为了阿米娅的一部分。","id":276},{"type":"Dialog","id":277},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":278},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":280},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_uptown_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":281},{"type":"Character","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"Text","text":"“拔刀之招，当破即破。”","id":284},{"type":"Dialog","id":285},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_victoria","screenadapt":"coverall","id":287},{"type":"Character","id":288},{"type":"Character","name":"char_222_bpipe","id":289},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"Text","text":"“泪锋之招，当断即断。”","id":291},{"type":"Dialog","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_lungmen_o","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"Character","id":295},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Text","text":"“泪锋之剑，当弃即弃。”","id":298},{"type":"Dialog","id":299},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cenbri","screenadapt":"coverall","id":301},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":302},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"Text","text":"“云裂之剑，当立则立。”","id":304},{"type":"Dialog","id":305},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":307},{"type":"skipnode","mode":"nofirstskip","id":308},{"type":"Dialog","id":309},{"type":"Character","id":310},{"type":"Subtitle","id":311},{"type":"theater","mode":"true","id":312},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_topburning","screenadapt":"coverall","id":313},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$amiyaevolution_intro","key":"$amiyaevolution_loop","volume":"0.4","crossfade":"5","id":315,"musicid":2},{"type":"Text","text":"更多的记忆坠入阿米娅的思绪，时代的洪流在阿米娅的思维中涌动。","id":316},{"type":"Text","text":"那不是个好结局。但阿米娅已经没有时间了。","id":317},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":318},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":319},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_7_2","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":320},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅看见陈的怒视。","id":322},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_9_1","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":323},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅看见塔露拉的火焰。","id":324},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅清楚，她们必须在这里解决这件事。","id":325},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":326},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_5_7_chen","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":327},{"type":"Text","text":"这把愤怒的剑不会只是过去的剑。它还必须是现在的剑。","id":328},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":329},{"type":"Dialog","id":330},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":332},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅握紧了剑柄。","id":333},{"type":"Dialog","id":334},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":335},{"type":"stopmusic","id":336},{"type":"Character","id":337},{"type":"Image","id":338},{"type":"Background","id":339},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"Video","res":"video/01.mp4","id":341},{"type":"theater","mode":"false","id":342},{"type":"skipnode","mode":"skip","id":343},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":344},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_topburning","fadetime":"2","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$amiyaevolution_loop","key":"$amiyaevolution_loop","volume":"0.4","id":346,"musicid":3},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":348},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......剑......","id":351,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"......剑。","id":353,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"从纺织转化成切割。蕴含的能量没有增加，形式却改变了。","id":354,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"真货。卡特斯，恭喜你。","id":355,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你不是什么碎片，不是实验品，不是模仿者。","id":356,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你的确是萨卡兹的君主......人类之敌。","id":357,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不，站在你面前的是一个感染者。","id":359,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"一个......人。","id":360,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#3","id":361},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我有点......说不出话。","id":362,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅，你这是......什么魔术？","id":363,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这个，现在应该不怎么重要......","id":365,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"确实。但其实挺重要的，事关尊严问题。为什么你拿着和赤霄几乎差不多像的剑？为什么你会我苦练了十几年的剑术？","id":367,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"（陈小姐......有这么严重吗？！）","id":369,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"闲话，下次再说。这把剑，有多像赤霄？","id":371,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你可以当它就是另一把赤霄。","id":373,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"好，阿米娅。你记得我多少剑术？","id":375,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"全都记得。我看在眼里，我从你的心里发现的，我全都记得。","id":377,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......你从我心里发现了什么？","id":379,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呃，陈小姐......不，不用担心，我只看了那些你希望我能学会的东西。我能判别这些事情，唔，也真的没看别的。","id":381,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"全忘掉吧。","id":383,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"魏彦吾总说，想使唤赤霄，归根结底不靠剑术，靠的是心境。","id":384,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我总当他乱讲嘢，但也还是得承认，他的剑术造诣，我这辈子都别想赶上。","id":385,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"所以，他在谈合作讲道理的时候你可以当他是放屁，但要用剑，就听我一回，听他一回！","id":386,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":387},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好的！","id":388,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"两把剑。你居然选择了赤霄这样恶毒的武器。","id":390,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"武器，哪有什么恶毒不恶毒？这大地上的武器，有哪一把能比你恶毒？","id":392,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅，听好......！","id":393,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"如果你的愤慨和我的怒火如出一辙，我们的剑就不分彼此！","id":394,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"上了，阿米娅！先不要管她死活！","id":395,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"啊？！真的可以吗......！","id":397,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":398},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"别想得我们好像真有得选一样！","id":399,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"这样的武器给了你们信心？","id":401,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"滑稽戏我今天已经看过一场，不想再看第二遍了。","id":402,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"试试你的剑吧，卡特斯。看看你的技术怎么样。","id":403,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":404},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":405},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.5","Delay":"0.4","id":406},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":407},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":408},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.4","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":409},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.4","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":410},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"1","g":"0.4","b":"0.1","afrom":"1","rfrom":"1","gfrom":"0.4","bfrom":"0.4","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":411},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0.8","rfrom":"1","gfrom":"1","bfrom":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.1","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":414},{"type":"Character","id":415},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"1","id":416},{"type":"Dialog","id":417},{"type":"Character","id":418},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":419},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"太慢了！赤霄！","id":420,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":421},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"拔刀！","id":422,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":423},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_37","screenadapt":"coverall","id":424},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"30","yTo":"30","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.6","yScaleTo":"1.6","duration":"0.01","block":"true","id":425},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":426},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":427},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":428},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":429},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":430},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-30","yTo":"-60","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"0.01","block":"true","id":431},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":432},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":433},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":434},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":435},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":436},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":437},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_37","screenadapt":"coverall","id":438},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":439},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":440},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"啊......","id":441,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":442},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"（凯尔希医生说的是真的，赤霄的确是能切开法术的剑......！）","id":443,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","id":444},{"type":"Dialog","id":445},{"type":"Text","text":"不断吞噬周遭事物的无形火焰，在青黑色与红色闪烁过后消散如无物。","id":446},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":447},{"type":"Dialog","id":448},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":449},{"type":"Image","id":450},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":451},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$blooddrop","id":452},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":453},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":454},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"伤口。","id":455,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"怎么会......","id":456,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"从我真正自恨意里重生到现在，这副身体尚不曾受到过一点伤害。","id":457,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":458},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"竟然只划到她的手指......她法术里蕴含的能量，实在是太大了！","id":459,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":460},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"别小看这一点点伤口！","id":461,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"每次你都给她留一个伤口，千百个伤口之后，她也就失血而死了！","id":462,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":463},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"这样说真让我伤心。","id":464,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"披着那张皮说这种话，你以为你是谁？","id":466,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":467},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"龙门近卫局真是培养了个好心肠。","id":468,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"和外人一起伤害亲人的身体，你很开心的样子，晖洁。","id":469,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你也敢这么叫我？","id":471,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":472},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你要是想杀我的话，就下手吧，晖洁。","id":473,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":474},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你......","id":475,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":476},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"我已经永远都回不去了。我恨这一切。我恨你。我恨养育你的这片土地。它把你变成这样。","id":477,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"杀了我吧，让我解脱吧。否则，我就会杀了你。","id":478,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"至少......至少......晖洁，晖洁......别让我动手杀你。我不想，我不能......","id":479,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"哪怕我是因为你才变成这样。","id":480,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":481},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......我......二十年前那一次，我......","id":482,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":483},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"是你不和我一起走。","id":484,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"是你逃了，是你退缩了，晖洁。我变成这个样子......变成这个我也厌恶的样子......都是因为你。","id":485,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"都是因为你。都是因为你答应过了却反悔了。","id":486,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":487},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"啊......","id":488,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":489},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"那个月夜，那个下着倾盆大雨的夜晚......","id":490,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你为什么心甘情愿地留在那条恶龙身边？","id":491,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"他杀了我爸，逼死我们的妈妈......害我们两人分离！","id":492,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"现在，你还要帮他做事？","id":493,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":494},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"它说谎！","id":495,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈小姐，你仔细想想......","id":496,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那天晚上究竟是什么样子？","id":497,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":498},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"......","id":499,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":500},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"那是个晴天。我绝对不会记错......那天晚上，虽然没有月亮，没有星星——","id":501,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但你拉我出去的时候，是白天。那天是白天。","id":502,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":503},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"也就是说......","id":504,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不。塔露拉，科西切的源石技艺不是在他死后才生效的......","id":505,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"他从那时候开始，就已经对你施用了这个法术了。","id":506,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"想一想吧。你有多少思绪被扭曲了，你有多少记忆被蒙上了薄纱？","id":507,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"就算他没篡改你的记忆，可是你记忆里那些不分明的东西，还是被他利用了！","id":508,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"塔露拉，如果你还是塔露拉的话——","id":509,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"哪怕你想要发动一场战争，哪怕你会牺牲很多人......","id":510,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你会为了自己，让他们毫无价值地死去吗？","id":511,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"如果真的要牺牲，你难道不才是那第一个吗？","id":512,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你会允许雪怪和霜星无助地死去吗？你会用爱国者保护着的东西去摧毁你尊敬的他吗？你会允许无数的乌萨斯人，无数的感染者，因此死去吗？","id":513,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":514},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"够了。你是撼动不了我的意志的。","id":515,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你们就连动作都一模一样，连节奏都吻合......我有点犯恶心。","id":516,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"这两把剑还奈何不了我。","id":517,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你们的体力会随着时间耗尽，我的火焰却是无穷无尽的。","id":518,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"剑是你们手足的伸展，而我就是力量本身。你们将被疲劳击垮，而我会取走你们的性命。","id":519,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":520},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"塔露拉，睁开眼睛看看吧......这样的结果，这样的惨剧，就是你想要的吗？","id":521,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这就是你想要的吗？！","id":522,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":523},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"够了！","id":524,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":525},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fireburst","volume":"1","text":"","id":526},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":527},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":528},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":529},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"藏在蛋壳里是没用的。面对我。","id":530,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅仰起头。","id":531},{"type":"Text","text":"她这样说，仿佛陈述事实。","id":532},{"type":"Dialog","id":533},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":534},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":535},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":536},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":537},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":538},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":539},{"type":"Text","text":"陈看了看阿米娅。身边的女孩已经和十分钟前的阿米娅判若两人。","id":540},{"type":"Text","text":"她反常的语气令人惊讶，那种感觉，像是有三分之一来自阿米娅本人，三分之一惟妙惟肖地学着自己，还有三分之一......","id":541},{"type":"Text","text":"陈也不知道那是什么东西。","id":542},{"type":"Dialog","id":543},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":544},{"type":"Text","text":"德拉克双唇紧闭。","id":545},{"type":"Text","text":"在多次吞吐词句后，她还是开口了。","id":546},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你又从谁那里看到了些什么景象？听到了什么遗言？","id":547,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"卡特斯，将死之人才喜欢复述业已腐朽的辞句。过去的一切都伤不了我。","id":548,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":549},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fireburst","volume":"1","text":"","id":550},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":551},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":552},{"type":"Text","text":"与此同时，她敲打着剑柄，轻轻拨开眼前晃动的空气，将高温泼洒向同是感染者的两人。","id":553},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":554},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":555},{"type":"Text","text":"陈大吼。就在她要出剑之前，她忽然觉得，也许这一剑让阿米娅来更好。","id":556},{"type":"Dialog","id":557},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":558},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"赤霄，奔夜！","id":559,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":560},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_chixiaobadao","id":561},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.02","block":"false","id":562},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"false","id":563},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#2","id":564},{"type":"Text","text":"她侧过头看着陈，笑了一笑。","id":565},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"呃，不好意思，是这样的剑术，没错吧？","id":566,"figure":"avg_npc_087#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":567},{"type":"Character","id":568},{"type":"Text","text":"蓝色？黑色......大概是青色。很好看。相比之下赤霄实在是太血腥了。","id":569},{"type":"Text","text":"陈这时心想，这场战斗也许就该这样。","id":570},{"type":"Text","text":"供氧装置已经在战斗中被焚毁，背着氧气盒子和一条火龙干架纯属是想炸死自己。","id":571},{"type":"Text","text":"陈没好气地丢掉了多余的装备，深感自己的准备规划还是做得过于草率。","id":572},{"type":"Dialog","id":573},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":574},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":575},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅，可没剩多少时间了，她打算把这里的氧气烧干。","id":576,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Text","text":"身旁的兔子同样也身经百战，这句提醒肯定是不必要的，但足够转移自己的注意力了。","id":577},{"type":"Text","text":"这么做的原因只有一个。陈要转移自己的注意力。陈深深地吸了一口气。","id":578},{"type":"Text","text":"现在的自己一点也不冷静。","id":579},{"type":"Text","text":"不甘被剑鞘束缚，锋芒暂敛的赤霄剑在匣中剧烈颤动，也像是为了之后那场猛烈的释放而压抑到癫狂。","id":580},{"type":"Text","text":"不过，很可能只是因为自己的手在颤抖。","id":581},{"type":"Text","text":"这么多年来，只有这次......只有这次，陈确实感受到了赤霄剑的强韧，她生怕自己握不住剑，却也不由得和这把剑一同狂喜。","id":582},{"type":"Text","text":"陈好像突然明白了。赤霄没有意志，赤霄的意志来自用剑的人。","id":583},{"type":"Text","text":"之前的她不是拔不出赤霄。她是没碰到那个必须要用这把剑的时候。","id":584},{"type":"Text","text":"而现在，面前的熊熊烈火，面前的恶棍，面前久违的友人，亲人与罪人，以及彻底的绝境，重重地压在了她身上。","id":585},{"type":"Text","text":"颤抖渐止，陈感觉已经是时候了。赤霄等得太久了。","id":586},{"type":"Text","text":"自己也等得太久了。","id":587},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":588},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈小姐，请等等。我们也许能伤害到她，我们可能有这种能力。就算我们能杀她也没用。","id":589,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":590},{"type":"Character","id":591},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅也觉得这不像是自己在说话。","id":592},{"type":"Text","text":"她像一把利刃，像一把被不公和惨事压弯了剑身的利刃，尽管如此，阿米娅却觉得，这利刃会弹回原状，锋利如初。","id":593},{"type":"Text","text":"她感觉自己有点像陈。","id":594},{"type":"Text","text":"也不坏。她终究不可能是陈。","id":595},{"type":"Text","text":"阿米娅望着塔露拉。","id":596},{"type":"Text","text":"陈小姐，以前你抓捕犯人，是为了鞭打他和侮辱他吗？是为了夺走他的生命吗？","id":597},{"type":"Text","text":"她的无名怒火却不像陈。她感到被背叛，感到被驱使，感到被孤立，她在历经一个尚未结束的故事，一个灰暗却依然还在的未来。","id":598},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":599},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那应该只是个结果，我想。何况我们并没那个权力。","id":600,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我知道，你会说，就这样洗脱她的嫌疑也太容易了。","id":601,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不，陈长官......陈小姐。不对。","id":602,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但她的嫌疑是否能洗脱，还要等到事解决之后。","id":603,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":604},{"type":"Text","text":"陈咬住嘴唇，直到出血。血亲相残，她怎么会为这种事感到喜悦？她说不清。","id":605},{"type":"Text","text":"她忍住没将赤霄举起。","id":606},{"type":"Text","text":"她叹了一口气。","id":607},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"没错。那只是结果。我首先要让他们罪有应得。死要留到判刑以后。","id":608,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_011_talula_1","id":609},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉？","text":"你们的信心是从哪里来的？","id":610,"figure":"char_011_talula_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":611},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这不叫信心，怪物。","id":612,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这叫责任。","id":613,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Text","text":"陈昂首挺胸。","id":614},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_087#3","id":615},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们有义务。","id":616,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"科西切，你却什么都没有。","id":617,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你的身躯是借来的，你的谎言会被戳穿，你的火焰在赤霄前摇摇欲坠。","id":618,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你把这里选作战场，盘踞在你的武器和伪装之上，你没有离开核心城，既是傲慢，也是愚鲁。","id":619,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你作茧自缚，已经无处可逃。","id":620,"figure":"avg_npc_087#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":621},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":622},{"type":"Image","id":623}],"characters":["塔露拉？","陈","阿米娅"]}